R = int(input())

# Find the minimum increase needed to move to the next tier
# Current tier boundaries: 0-99 (1 ^), 100-199 (2 ^), 200-299 (3 ^), 300-399 (4 ^)

if R < 100:
    next_threshold = 100
elif R < 200:
    next_threshold = 200
else:  # R < 300
    next_threshold = 300

increase = next_threshold - R
print(increase)
